nodes.text: The Western Watchwoods was the name given to the western part of the forest located on the northern edge of the Gormak Lands on the planet Voss, at the foot of the mountain where Voss-Ka was located. The resurgent Sith Empire's Outpost Skyline was located on the western edge of the Western Watchwoods, while the Koss Overlook marked the border between the Western and Eastern Watchwoods.
